{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because in Poland, the cigarettes-- in Warsaw, the cigarettes were very expensive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I knew how this procedure was going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in this office, there was an older soldier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a surgeon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was such a-- a military bureaucrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was keeping those documents in his desk and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And every time when I-- when I need a document for the-- for one of these Polish-- Polish guys going back to Warsaw, I had to go to his office and ask and explain and so on that I was given such a document.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes, Liliana was also going with me, just for-- for relaxation and for curiosity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- those particular-- this particular person was quite-- quite friendly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, he didn't suspect anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, when we already decided that we have to get out of this city, we came to this soldier or to this German soldier.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were talking in different aspect and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, we managed that he had to go to the other room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were several rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was sitting at the desk in-- in one room, in the first room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he went to the other room, Lilian sneaked to his desk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- because she knew where those documents-- those travel documents were lying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she took one travel document-- document.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just stole the document.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The documents were already signed, but only the name was not filled in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she took it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there's-- there's the-- apparently, the next time when we had to go, he was complaining that he'd counted those documents.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
